    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>General description:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Unlighted</strong> you will play as a test subject that works for  called <i>Umbral Alchemy</i>, a company dedicated to the research of stones with mysterious properties never seen before by humans. Thanks to you they hope to discover the origin of these strange materials, but it won't be an easy path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/2340f2c785a2906cfde482b48a056eb4.poster.avif?t=1764532548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/2340f2c785a2906cfde482b48a056eb4.webm?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/2340f2c785a2906cfde482b48a056eb4.mp4?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a test subject you will have to test your abilities to advance through the different tests that the scientists of <i>Umbral Alchemy</i> will set you. If you manage to survive, which is highly improbable, you will be remembered as a hero who has managed to solve the greatest mystery of mankind, or at least of those who know about the existence of the Umbralita rocks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/9950f7aafbdc3c61ffff90d0f78695ae.poster.avif?t=1764532548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/9950f7aafbdc3c61ffff90d0f78695ae.webm?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/9950f7aafbdc3c61ffff90d0f78695ae.mp4?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will solve puzzles in first person using a scanner for given by <i>Umbral Alchemy</i>. With a minimalist and oppressive graphic style, accompanied by sounds and music that will create nerves, tension and an eerie feeling through the tests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/a7519bc24b43ba4605b9603e16c4a914.poster.avif?t=1764532548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/a7519bc24b43ba4605b9603e16c4a914.webm?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/a7519bc24b43ba4605b9603e16c4a914.mp4?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By using the scanner, you will have to observe where the key parts will be to solve the puzzles that <i>Umbral Alchemy</i> will pose. Make the Umbralita appear to succeed on the tests that Bill presents to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/b0820c08a90a2489508905ac8f15a5cd.poster.avif?t=1764532548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/b0820c08a90a2489508905ac8f15a5cd.webm?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/b0820c08a90a2489508905ac8f15a5cd.mp4?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game modes:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single player first person story mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/6e4ec918b03a2a8fbbd9dadce3fa35f1.poster.avif?t=1764532548\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/6e4ec918b03a2a8fbbd9dadce3fa35f1.webm?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051520/extras/6e4ec918b03a2a8fbbd9dadce3fa35f1.mp4?t=1764532548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Content:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you enter the Unlighted project, you will have to solve about 20 different puzzles. It will not include DLC's. Will not include cosmetics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrades and Support:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently there will be no DLC's in the future. We will continue updating and giving post-release support, fixing the necessary problems.</p>",
